6879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8c1f56dbdf04acf40df6768b787733eba1ff98f","tid":1364005,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"但係三人或以上又會非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"啱呀 睇到我頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"呢個咪就係警察國家嘅特色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將法例寫到無限闊 基本上你只要呼吸 就有坐監嘅可能性 而平時唔拉你 只係某種恩賜<br />\n<br />\n係時候放低你本普通法法例啦，做好孭gear入去就有入臭格嘅風險，光復元朗<br />\n<br />\nbe tough my friend, never back off."},{"pid":"9a00e7a99cecc806e76212c18969580a32b30949","tid":1364005,"uid":178939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8c1f56dbdf04acf40df6768b787733eba1ff98f","tid":1364005,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"但係三人或以上又會非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"如果係和平集會/遊行，要三十人遊行或五十人集會，沒有通知警方，為非法集會。判刑相對較輕。<br />\n<br />\n三人以上嗰條係非法集結，除左要有三人之外仲要係符合以下資格：<br />\n<br />\n《公安條例》第18條，「非法集結」的定義是凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作擾亂秩序的行為或作帶有威嚇、侮辱或挑撥的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕集結者會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，即屬非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果係一般遊行，要三十人以上先可以係非法集會。"},{"pid":"3d37951175c2f768abf67cf9d1e338d748c5df69","tid":1364005,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0217a0f92f3e19808acfb867df07ad3a3caad7b6","tid":1364005,"uid":46879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8c1f56dbdf04acf40df6768b787733eba1ff98f","tid":1364005,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"但係三人或以上又會非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"啱呀 睇到我頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"拒絕服從禁止集會或遊行命令<br />\n刑罰係第3級罰款及監禁12個月<br />\nref. 第245章 《公安條例》 第17A條<br />\n<br />\n非法集結係另一條重好多嘅罪嚟<br />\n當中必需包括破壞社會安寧或威嚇性行為等元素<br />\n一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年<br />\n一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁3年<br />\nref. 第245章 《公安條例》 第18條"},{"pid":"745f5472e25be8ddc572e799e6cd65b3bfcc41ec","tid":1364005,"uid":44461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b964da26db271f50d8fb44b70f5a6ab13755338","tid":1364005,"uid":44461,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0217a0f92f3e19808acfb867df07ad3a3caad7b6","tid":1364005,"uid":46879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8c1f56dbdf04acf40df6768b787733eba1ff98f","tid":1364005,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"但係三人或以上又會非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"啱呀 睇到我頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"呢個咪就係警察國家嘅特色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將法例寫到無限闊 基本上你只要呼吸 就有坐監嘅可能性 而平時唔拉你 只係某種恩賜<br />\n<br />\n係時候放低你本普通法法例啦，做好孭gear入去就有入臭格嘅風險，光復元朗<br />\n<br />\nbe tough my friend, never back off."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"負評我嘅唔洗收埋啦，即管出黎討論下，我地一齊黎重溫下長毛點樣自己一個人非法集結:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.hkgolden.com/view_amp.aspx%3fmessage=4175122&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview_amp.aspx%253fmessage%3D4175122%26page%3D1&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6ae24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=837b8935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.hkgolden.com/view_amp.aspx%3fmessage=4175122&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n我重申我唔係叫人唔好出去，相反我極力支持大家出去，我自己都會去買老婆餅，但今次連不反對通知書都無，講真已經無「和理非行街街」嘅灰色地帶，你帶住頭盔同豬嘴，佢一睇就知你唔係街坊，的你入臭格48個鐘放返你出去又有幾奇?<br />\n<br />\n如果你呢家仲相信香港呢家有法治嘅就真係too simple sometimes naive 啦，呢幾年律政司點樣亂告人大家唔洗我多提，堅守住嘅只有少數港英年代高院同終院嘅官，基本上香港係示威相關嘅法律系統，已經完全咁淪陷左。如果你想重溫嘅，不妨去睇下少女點樣用胸部襲擊警員?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真話永遠都係殘酷嘅，你帶得頭盔豬嘴出去，個日就有一定風險俾狗亂拉，但你更加唔應該退縮，應該要正面咁對抗呢個強權。"},{"pid":"7c1def16817d63950e870db83bccaded4b775ec3","tid":1364005,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d37951175c2f768abf67cf9d1e338d748c5df69","tid":1364005,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0217a0f92f3e19808acfb867df07ad3a3caad7b6","tid":1364005,"uid":46879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8c1f56dbdf04acf40df6768b787733eba1ff98f","tid":1364005,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"但係三人或以上又會非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"啱呀 睇到我頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"拒絕服從禁止集會或遊行命令<br />\n刑罰係第3級罰款及監禁12個月<br />\nref. 第245章 《公安條例》 第17A條<br />\n<br />\n非法集結係另一條重好多嘅罪嚟<br />\n當中必需包括破壞社會安寧或威嚇性行為等元素<br />\n一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年<br />\n一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁3年<br />\nref. 第245章 《公安條例》 第18條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n如果違反禁止集會遊行命令之餘再進行召集的話刑罰會變重<br />\n可相當於非法集結<br />\n<br />\n所以就有否進行號召呢點罰則會有相當差異"},{"pid":"18b5d7cecbe8e97d2daae37f331e57e1276d7f1f","tid":1364005,"uid":38550,"like":1,"dislike